    <h4>Korean Platinum</h4>
    <div>
      <ul>
        <li>In Korean Platinum, Pokédex entries also exist in Korean, for a total of 7 languages (Korean, English, Japanese, French, Italian, German, and Spanish).</li>
        <li>Korean DS games can't trade with Non-Korean DS games.</li>
        <li>Korean DS games can trade with GBA games of any language.</li>
        <li>It is possible to obtain all Pokédex entries in all languages because DS events were also released in Korea.</li>
        <li>Korean Mew can't be obtained from My Pokémon Ranch, because My Pokémon Ranch doesn't exist in Korean. An event if required.</li>
      </ul>
